    <h2>General Questions</h2>
    <h3>Q: What is a Blood Bank Management System?</h3>
    <p>A: The Blood Bank Management System is a software solution designed to streamline the process of managing blood donation activities, including donor registration, inventory management, and distribution of blood products to healthcare facilities.</p>

    <h3>Q: How can I register as a blood donor?</h3>
    <p>A: To register as a blood donor, visit our website and make your account by sign up button and when you done all the formalities in sign-up portion you can log in by your username and password and then click on login. Follow the provided instructions to complete the registration form. Once registered, you can log in and schedule your donation appointments.</p>

